<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>A Two Time All-American Hurdler Overcomes Obstacles in Sports and Business</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="A Two Time All-American Hurdler Overcomes Obstacles in Sports and Business" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160509132542-the-ground-guys-justin-rush.jpeg" rel="share" />

											<div class="caption info">
